casebody.data:
Jane DOE NO. 62, Plaintiff,
v.
INDIANA UNIVERSITY BLOOMINGTON, et al., Defendants. Supreme Court Case No. 18S-CQ-00220 Supreme Court of Indiana. Filed June 01, 2018

Order

Pursuant to Indiana Appellate Rule 64, the United States District Court for the Southern District of Indiana has certified several questions of Indiana state law arising in Jane Doe No. 62 v. Indiana University Bloomington, et al. , Case No. 1:16-CV-01480-JMS-DML for this Court's consideration.

The certified questions, which each member of this Court has considered, are hereby DECLINED by a majority vote of the Court.
